00:56:10,000 --> 00:56:16,000
but necessarily so.

431
00:56:18,000 --> 00:56:20,000
And of course, I'm all for that.

432
00:56:20,000 --> 00:56:24,000
We're bypassing the modalities.

433
00:56:28,000 --> 00:56:38,000
Right, I'm just trying to put the case for the idea

