01:06:39,000 --> 01:06:46,000
And what Tarski did was to do something to give an account of truth for languages,

541
01:06:46,000 --> 01:06:52,000
unlike natural languages which were capable of variable interpretations.

542
01:06:52,000 --> 01:06:59,000
So the Tarski definition is an account of how you take a semantics

